text.div:
Snomed-CT Body Structures

This value set includes all the "Clinical finding" Snomed-CT codes (i.e. codes with an is-a relationship with 91723000: Anatomical structure)

This value set includes codes defined in other code systems, using the following rules:

  • Include codes from http://snomed.info/id where concept is-a 91723000
